							<h1>あなたはどっち？「話がわかりやすい人」と「わかりにくい人」の違い8か条</h1>
							<p class="catch"><img width="655" height="437" src="http://211.125.65.24/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/1021.jpg" class="attachment-detail-img wp-post-image" alt="102" /></p>
						</div><!-- /box_title -->

												<div class="ad">
							<!--mclude /wp-content/themes/lig2013/single_top_ad.php -->
<!-- EBiS 3pas tag version 0.00 start -->
<script type="text/javascript">
